snippet.textDisplay:
What a fantastic start to Coke Studio Bangla! This is exactly what I hoping it would be...  
-the words/lyrics already exist in the many beautiful languages that are spoken in Bangladesh, all they require is the unique and rare touch of musical genius in order to transform them into something more fun, more relatable and modern- 
'Nasek Nasek' ticks all of the boxes (along with being a straight up anthem level song), not surprising considering the unbelievable wealth of that music geniuses that have been gathered for this project. Keep it coming!
